00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:30.199
Sometimes we think it's all about us

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:32.520
coming in and preaching to people,

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:35.119
but honestly, we get our lives marked.

00:03:35.119 --> 00:03:37.360
We get our lives impacted.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:40.479
And this has just been such a positive

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:42.679
several days to be part of here.

00:03:42.679 --> 00:03:45.960
So thank you for all that you do and who you are

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:48.000
and what God is doing in this place.

00:03:48.679 --> 00:03:51.199
You're really a blessing to people that come through.

00:03:51.199 --> 00:03:52.039
Thanks.

00:03:52.039 --> 00:03:53.520
You encouraged us.

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:54.679
All right, that's the nice stuff.

