00:31:01.899 --> 00:31:04.339
each person, there were about 20 of us in the room,

00:31:04.339 --> 00:31:07.299
we were given seven minutes to preach a sermon,

00:31:07.299 --> 00:31:10.039
to put together a sermon and preach the sermon.

