00:37:12.499 --> 00:37:15.059
beyond our thoughts and our capability,

00:37:15.059 --> 00:37:17.579
that woman will have a testimony.

00:37:17.579 --> 00:37:21.579
God spoke to me and did something in my heart.

00:37:21.579 --> 00:37:25.579
I had a peace that it passed understanding.

00:37:25.619 --> 00:37:26.459
Amen.

00:37:27.539 --> 00:37:30.299
