Yeah, that's right.

00:37:32.779 --> 00:37:34.019
Where are the people?

00:37:34.019 --> 00:37:37.859
Where are the believers that will step up and say,

00:37:39.139 --> 00:37:41.139
I'm willing to experience that?

00:37:42.279 --> 00:37:44.259
Because God promises that.

00:37:45.139 --> 00:37:50.139
A peace that passes understanding

00:37:50.539 --> 00:37:53.059
in the very midst of the worst storm

00:37:54.019 --> 00:37:55.739
that we can possibly think.

