We already talked about power.

00:38:16.459 --> 00:38:17.399
Oh, wait a minute.

00:38:17.399 --> 00:38:19.219
Ye shall receive power

00:38:19.219 --> 00:38:21.939
after that the Holy Ghost has come upon you

00:38:21.939 --> 00:38:26.059
and ye shall be my witnesses unto me,

00:38:26.059 --> 00:38:31.059
both at the same time in Jerusalem.

