Hey, if you're an apostle,

00:38:33.940 --> 00:38:36.899
what a great thing to hear.

00:38:36.899 --> 00:38:39.779
I'm gonna witness about Jesus in Jerusalem

00:38:39.779 --> 00:38:42.419
where they just crucified him.

