How does a Jew who has been with Jesus

00:39:18.099 --> 00:39:20.539
and he's a disciple, an apostle,

00:39:21.219 --> 00:39:22.579
how does he go into Jerusalem

00:39:22.579 --> 00:39:25.339
and preach the gospel to the Pharisees?

