How does he go up to Samaria?

00:39:35.940 --> 00:39:39.899
The Samaritans hate him and they hate them.

00:39:41.339 --> 00:39:44.259
And I'm supposed to walk into Samaria

00:39:44.259 --> 00:39:45.619
and preach the gospel

00:39:45.619 --> 00:39:48.579
and they're gonna listen to me, a converted Jew?

00:39:48.579 --> 00:39:51.539
Yeah, because it's not about you.

00:39:51.539 --> 00:39:53.579
It's about the Spirit of God

00:39:53.579 --> 00:39:56.859
empowering the message of the gospel.

